{
  "stem": "3206.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never heard of him, because when my mother separated from him when I was very young, maybe two or three years old.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's about it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Staszow, he wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a very sick man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had asthma, and he couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But before that, before he got married the second time, he was a merchant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a store, [? lettuce ?] store, what they say-- a store in that small town, Bogoria.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had a store, and that's what the family made a living from.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was quite good in it, and you know, they made a living.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when I came back, he wasn't working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our brothers were working, like Haskel, my sister, and my brother, which is here, Karl, they were working.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were working at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were shoemakers, like making the tops of shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], that's what they called that at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were working, contracting for a big storekeeper, which he had shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was selling shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was helping as much as he could, and that's what we made a living from.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was he like as a father?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was he lenient?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was he strict?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as a father I can tell you that-- a father, you know-- that he never bothered too much with me, you know, because he was himself not-- whatever I did was OK-- not too direct or-- like here a father is, like, I notice in my own son-in-law, you know, his boy comes home from school, what did you do?",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did you do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And come on, I want to hear what you know, how you're learning, things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not my father, no. it was just plain and simple.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
